<MethodEndpoint
  method={"get"}
  path={"/registry/beta/campaigns/{id}/orders"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



Returns a list of the phone number assignment orders for a campaign.
The orders are returned sorted by creation date, with the most recent
appearing first. The list is filterable by sending in any of the
following parameters.

#### Permissions
The API token must include the following scopes: _Messaging_.
